# Khuzhir, Okinsky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Khuzhir (; , Khujar) is a rural locality (a selo) in Okinsky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 625 as of 2010. There are 9 streets.
Geography
Khuzhir is located 55&nbsp;km north of Orlik (the district's administrative centre) by road. Shuluta-Tala is the nearest rural locality.
